Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: Я готов отвечать. ([subtitled] Ready to comply.)

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [on radio] All right, what do you see?

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Standard beat cops. Small station. Quiet street. It’s a good target.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: There’s an ATM in the south corner, which means . . .

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Cameras.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Both cross streets are one way.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: So, compromised escape routes.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Means our guy doesn't care about being seen, he isn't afraid to make a mess on the way out. You see that Range Rover halfway up the block?

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Yeah, the red one? It’s cute.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: [on radio] It's also bulletproof, which means private security, which means more guns, which means more headaches for somebody. Probably us.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: You guys know I can move things with my mind, right?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Looking over your shoulder needs to become second nature.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Anybody ever tell you you're a little paranoid?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Not to my face. Why? Did you hear something?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Eyes on target, folks. This is the best lead we've had on Rumlow in six months. I don't want to lose him.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: If he sees us coming that won't be a problem. He kind of hates us.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Sam, see that garbage truck? Tag it.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Give me X-ray.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: That truck’s loaded for max weight. And the driver’s armed.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: It’s a battering ram.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Go now.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: What?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: He’s not hitting the police.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Body armor, AR-15's. I make seven hostiles.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: I make 5.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Sam.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Four.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Rumlow’s on the third floor.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Wanda, just like we practiced.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: What about the gas?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Get it out.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Rumlow has a biological weapon.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: (on radio) I’m on it.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Sam. He's in an AFV heading north.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: I got four, they're splitting up.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: I got the two on the left.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: They ditched their gear. It's a shell game now. One of them has the payload.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: He doesn't have it. I’m empty.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Out of the way!

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Payload secure. Thanks, Sam.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Don't thank me.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: I’m… not thanking that thing.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: His name is Redwing.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: I'm still not thanking it.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: He's cute. Go ahead, pet him.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Who's your buyer?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: What did you say?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Oh my . . . [Steve stares up, open mouthed.] Sam . . . We need . . . Fire and Rescue . . . on the south side of the building. We gotta get up there.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: That's how I wished it happened. Binarily Augmented Retro-Framing, or BARF. God, I gotta work on that acronym. An extremely costly method of hijacking the hippocampus to . . . clear traumatic memories. Huh.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: It doesn't change the fact that they never made it to the airport . . . or all the things I did to avoid processing my grief, but . . . [He takes off his glasses.] Plus, 611 million dollars for my little therapeutic experiment? No one in the right mind would've ever funded it.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Help me out, what's the MIT mission statement? "To generate, disseminate . . . and preserve knowledge. And work with others . . . to bring it to bear on the world's great challenges." Well, you are the others. And, quiet as it's kept . . . the challenges facing you are the greatest mankind's ever known. Plus, most of you are broke.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Oh, I'm sorry. Rather, you were. As of this moment . . . every student has been made an equal recipient of the Inaugural September Foundation Grant. As in . . . all of your projects have just been approved and funded.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: No strings, no taxes… just re-frame the future! Starting now.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Go break some eggs.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Restroom's this way, yeah?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: It's . . . fine. I'll be right back.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Ah, they deserve it. Plus, it helps ease my conscience.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Are you going up?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Okay, okay. Hey! Sorry, it's an occupational hazard.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: It's my fault.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: That's not true.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Turn the TV back on. They're being very specific.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: I should've clocked that bomb vest long before you had to deal with it.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Rumlow said "Bucky" and . . . all of a sudden I was a 16-year-old kid again, in Brooklyn. [He sits beside Wanda.]

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: And people died. It's on me.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: It's on both of us.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: This job . . . we try to save as many people as we can. Sometimes that doesn't mean everybody. But if we can't find a way to live with that, next time . . . maybe nobody gets saved.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Vis! We talked about this.

Name: Vision
Line: Yes, but the door was open so I assumed that . . .

Name: Vision
Line: Captain Rogers wished to know when Mr. Stark was arriving.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Thank you. We'll be right down.

Name: Vision
Line: I'll . . . use the door. Oh, and apparently, he's brought a guest.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: We know who it is?

Name: Vision
Line: The Secretary of State.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: Five years ago, I had a heart attack. I dropped right in the middle of my back-swing. Turned out it was the best round of my life, because after 13 hours of surgery and a triple bypass . . . I found something 40 years in the Army had never taught me

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: And what word would you use, Mr. Secretary?

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: How about "dangerous"? What would you call a group of US-based, enhanced individuals who routinely ignore sovereign borders and inflict their will wherever they choose and who, frankly, seem unconcerned about what they leave behind?

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: New York.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: Washington DC.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: Sokovia.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: Lagos.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Okay. That's enough.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: For the past four years, you've operated with unlimited power and no supervision. That's an arrangement the governments of the world can no longer tolerate. But I think we have a solution. [he places a thick document on the desk and passes it to Wanda]

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: The Sokovia Accords. Approved by 117 countries . . . it states that the Avengers shall no longer be a private organization. Instead, they'll operate under the supervision of a United Nations panel, only when and if that panel deems it necessary.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: The Avengers were formed to make the world a safer place. I feel we've done that.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: Tell me, Captain, do you know where Thor and Banner are right now?

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: If I misplaced a couple of 30 megaton nukes . . . you can bet there'd be consequences. Compromise. Reassurance. That's how the world works. Believe me, this is the middle ground.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: So, there are contingencies.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: Three days from now, the UN meets in Vienna to ratify the Accords.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: Talk it over.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: And if we come to a decision you don't like?

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: Then you retire.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Hello? Is this your car out front?

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: I jumped the curb.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Maybe we could take care of it ourselves. If you wanna call the cops, tha--that's okay too, I guess.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Thank you.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: You have kept your looks, Colonel. Congratulations.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: "Mission report

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: My name is Zemo. I will repeat my question. Mission report. December 16, 1991.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: When SHIELD fell, Black Widow released HYDRA files to the public. Millions of pages much of it encrypted, not easy to decipher. But . . . I have experience. And patience. A man can do anything if he has those.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Mission report. December 16. 1991.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: HYDRA deserves its place on the ash heap. So your death would not bother me. But I'd have to use this book . . . and other bloodier methods to find what I need. I don't look forward to that. You'd only be dying for . . . your pride.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Secretary Ross has a Congressional Medal of Honor, which is one more than you have.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: So let's say we agree to this thing. How long is it gonna be before they LoJack us like a bunch of common criminals?

Name: James Rhodes
Line: A 117 countries want to sign this. 117, Sam, and you're just like, "No, that's cool. We got it. "

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: How long are you going to play both sides?

Name: Vision
Line: I have an equation.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Oh, this will clear it up.

Name: Vision
Line: In the eight years since Mr. Stark announced himself as Iron Man, the number of known enhanced persons has grown exponentially. And during the same period, the number of potentially world-ending events has risen at a commensurate rate.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Are you saying it's our fault?

Name: Vision
Line: I'm saying there may be a causality. Our very strength invites challenge. Challenge incites conflict. And conflict . . . breeds catastrophe. Oversight . . . oversight is not an idea that can be dismissed out of hand.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Boom.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Tony. You are being uncharacteristically non-hyper-verbal.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: It's because he's already made up his mind.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Boy, you know me so well.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Actually, I'm nursing an electromagnetic headache.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: That's what's going on, Cap. It's just pain. It's discomfort. Who's putting coffee grounds in the disposal? Am I running a bed and breakfast for a biker gang?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Oh, that's Charles Spencer, by the way. He's a great kid. Computer engineering degree, 3.6 GPA. Had a floor level gig at Intel planned for the fall. But first, he wanted to put a few miles on his soul, before he parked it behind a desk. See the world. Maybe be of service. Charlie didn't want to go to Vegas or Fort Lauderdale, which is what I would do. He didn't go to Paris or Amsterdam, which sounds fun. He decided to spend his summer building sustainable housing for the poor. Guess where, Sokovia.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: He wanted to make a difference, I suppose. I mean, we won't know because we dropped a building on him while we were kicking ass. [He takes a pill with some coffee, then faces the others.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: There's no decision-making process here. We need to be put in check! Whatever form that takes, I'm game. If we can't accept limitations, if we're boundary-less, we're no better than the bad guys.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Tony, someone dies on your watch, you don't give up.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Who said we're giving up?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: We are if we're not taking responsibility for our actions. This document just shifts the blames.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: I'm sorry. Steve. That - that is dangerously arrogant. This is the United Nations we're talking about. It's not the World Security Council, it's not SHIELD, it's not HYDRA.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: No, but it's run by people with agendas, and agendas change.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: That's good. That's why I'm here. When I realized what my weapons were capable of in the wrong hands, I shut it down and stop manufacturing.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Tony, you chose to do that. If we sign this, we surrender our right to choose. What if this panel sends us somewhere we don't think we should go? What if there is somewhere we need to go, and they don't let us? We may not be perfect, but the safest hands are still our own.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: If we don't do this now, it's gonna be done to us later. That's the fact. That won't be pretty.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: You're saying they'll come for me.

Name: Vision
Line: We would protect you.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Maybe Tony's right.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: If we have one hand on the wheel, we can still steer. If we take it off -

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Aren't you the same woman who told the government to kiss her ass a few years ago?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: I'm just . . . I'm reading the terrain. We have made . . . some very public mistakes. We need to win their trust back.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Focus up. I'm sorry, did I just mishear you or did you agree with me?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Oh, I want to take it back now.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: No, no, no. You can't retract it. Thank you. Unprecedented. Okay, case closed--I win.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: I have to go.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: Margaret Carter was known to most as a founder of SHIELD . . . but I just knew her as Aunt Peggy.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: She had a photograph in her office. Aunt Peggy standing next to JFK. As a kid, that was pretty cool. But it was a lot to live up to. Which is why I never told anyone we were related.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: I asked her once how she managed to master diplomacy and espionage in a time when no one wanted to see a woman succeed at either. And she said, compromise where you can. But where you can't, don't. Even if everyone is telling you that something wrong is something right. Even if the whole world is telling you to move . . . it is your duty to plant yourself like a tree, look them in they eye and say " No, you move."

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: When I came out of the ice, I thought everyone I had known was gone. Then I found out that she was alive. I was just lucky to have her.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: She had you back, too.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Who else signed?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Tony. Rhodey. Vision.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Clint?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Says he's retired.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Wanda?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: TBD (To Be Determined). I'm off to Vienna for the signing of the Accords. There's plenty of room on the jet.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Just because it's the path of least resistance doesn't mean it's the wrong path. Staying together is more important than how we stay together.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: What are we giving up to do it?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: I'm sorry, Nat. I can't sign it.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: I know.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Then what are you doing here?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: I didn't want you to be alone.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Come here.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Yes?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Thanks.

Name: T'Challa
Line: I suppose neither of us is used to the spotlight.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Oh, well, it's not always so flattering.

Name: T'Challa
Line: You seem to be doing alright so far. Considering your last trip to Capitol Hill . . . I wouldn't think you would be particularly comfortable in this company.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Well, I'm not.

Name: T'Challa
Line: That alone makes me glad you're here, Miss Romanoff.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Why? You don't approve of all this?

Name: T'Challa
Line: The Accords, yes. The politics, not really. Two people in a room can get more done than a hundred.

Name: T'Challa
Line: Father.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: King T'Chaka. Please, allow me to apologize for what happened in Nigeria.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Yes, so am I.

Name: T'Challa
Line: That is the future calling. Such a pleasure.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Thank you. [Natasha goes.]

Name: T'Challa
Line: I'm happy, Father.

Name: T'Challa
Line: Thank you.

Name: T'Challa
Line: EVERYBODY GET DOWN!

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: My mom tried to talk me out of enlisting, but, um, not Aunt Peggy. She bought me my first thigh holster.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Very practical.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: And stylish. [Sharon and Steve wait by an elevator. They stand facing each other.]

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: CIA has you stationed over here now?

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: In Berlin, Joint Terrorism Task Force.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Right. Right. Sounds fun.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: I know, right?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Steve nods and smiles at Sharon.] I've been meaning to ask you. When you were spying on me from across the hall . . . .

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: You mean when I was doing my job.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Did Peggy know?

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: She kept so many secrets. I didn't want her to have one from you. [The elevator arrives.] Thanks for walking me back.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Sure. [Sam comes over.]

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Steve. There's something you gotta see.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: Who's coordinating?

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: Good. They're solid. Forensics?

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: I have to go to work.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: Call MI-6, see if we can get Micro Forensics to hurry this up. We need the whole team here in two hours or it's not worth it. [Sharon strides through with a man in a green jumpsuit. They pass T'Challa who sits on a bench looking stunned. There's a cut on his head. Natasha sits on the next bench along.]

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: I'm very sorry.

Name: T'Challa
Line: [He glances at her. He's holding an ornate silver ring which he toys with between his fingers.] In my culture death is not the end. It's more of a . . . stepping-off point. You reach out with both hands and Bast and Sekhmet, they lead you into the green veldt where . . . you can run forever.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: That sounds very peaceful.

Name: T'Challa
Line: My father thought so. [He puts the ring on his finger.] I am not my father.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: T'Challa. Task force will decide who brings in Barnes.

Name: T'Challa
Line: [He clenches his fist.] Don't bother, Miss Romanoff. I'll kill him myself. [He walks away.]

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Yeah?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You alright?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Ah, yeah, thanks. I got lucky. [Frowning she looks around, then stands up.] I know how much Barnes means to you. I really do. Stay home. You'll only make this worse. For all of us. Please.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Are you saying you'll arrest me?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: No. Someone will. If you interfere. That's how it works now.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: If he's this far gone, Nat, I should be the one to bring him in.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Why?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Because I'm the one least likely to die trying. [Not far away Steve ends the call.]

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Shit.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: She tell you to stay out of it? [He's also in a cap and shades.] Might have a point.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: He'd do it for me.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: 1945, maybe. I just want to make sure we considered all our options. The people that shoot at you usually wind up shooting at me. [Sharon arrives by Steve.]

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: Tips have been pouring in since that footage went public. Everybody thinks the Winter soldier goes to their gym. Most of it's noise. Except for this. [She slides Steve a file.] My boss expects a briefing, pretty much now . . . so that's all the head start you're gonna get.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Thank you.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: And you're gonna have to hurry. We have orders to shoot on sight.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Возвращение на Родину. Возвращение на Родину. Один. Один. Грузовой вагон… Грузовой вагон. Грузов- ([subtitled] Homecoming. One. One. Fright Car.) [Knocking at the door. He puts the book in a drawer and goes to the door. He reaches for a gun tucked in the back of his trouser and cocks it.]

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Ich konnte es schon von weitem riechen. Danke. ([subtitled] I could smell it before I opened the door. Thank you.)

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Bitte sehr, das ist wunderbar. ([subtitled] It's okay. This is wonderful.)

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Nein, nein. Das geht schon. Ich mach das. Vielen Dank, Frau Leiber. ([subtitled] No, no. It's okay. I can manage. Thank you Mrs. Leiber.) [Zemo closes the door. In the room is a large device with a cage at the bottom and a drum of coppered wire on top.]

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: [talking to the vendor in Romanian] ([assumed translation] How are they? Are they good? Give me six, thank you.[2])

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: [on radio] Heads up, Cap. German Special Forces, approaching from the south.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Understood. [Bucky's standing behind Steve. Steve slowly turns around to face him.] Do you know me?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: [Bucky stares at him.] You're Steve. I read about you in a museum.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: They've set the perimeter.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: I know you're nervous. And you have plenty of reason to be. But you're lying.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: I wasn't in Vienna. I don't do that anymore.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: They're entering the building.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Well, the people who think you did are coming here now. And they're not planning on taking you alive.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: That's smart. Good strategy.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: They're on the roof. I'm compromised.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: This doesn't have end in a fight, Buck.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: It always ends in a fight.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: 5 seconds.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You pulled me from the river. Why?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: I don't know.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: 3 seconds!

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Yes, you do.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Breach! Breach! Breach! [A grenade crashes through the window. Bucky kicks it to Steve, and he smothers it with his shield.]

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Buck, stop! You're gonna kill someone.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: [Bucky slams Steve down and punches a hole in the floor.] I'm not gonna kill anyone.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Come on, man.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Sam, southwest rooftop.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Who the hell's the other guy?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: About to find out.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Sam.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Got him. [Sam flies down and shoves the chopper off course. Then swoops towards street level.]

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Sam, I can't shake this guy.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Right behind you.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Stand down, now. [Bucky stands beside Steve who puts his shield on his back.] Congratulations, Cap. You're a criminal. [Police move in and force Bucky to his knees. Black Panther raises his hands. A cop moves Steve's arms behind his back. Black Panther retracts his claws and pulls off his mask revealing his face. It's T'Challa. Steve and Rhodes look curious.]

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Your highness. [Bucky's hauled flat on the ground.]

Name: Vision
Line: 'A pinch of paprika.' A pinch. [He adds a pinch. Wanda strolls in.]

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Is that paprikash?

Name: Vision
Line: I thought it might . . . lift your spirits.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: [She chuckles, stirs the ingredients in the pan with a spoon. She lifts the spoon to her lips, blows and has a taste. She smiles.] Spirits lifted.

Name: Vision
Line: In my defense, I haven't actually ever . . . eaten anything before, so . . .

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: May I?

Name: Vision
Line: Please. Wanda?

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Hmm.

Name: Vision
Line: No one dislikes you, Wanda. [She frowns curiously.]

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Thanks.

Name: Vision
Line: Oh, you're welcome. No, it's a . . . involuntary response in their amygdala. They can't help but be afraid of you.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Are you?

Name: Vision
Line: My amygdala is synthetic, so . . . [Wanda laughs.]

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: I used to think of myself one way. But after this . . . [her fingers glow.] I am something else. I'm still me, I think, but . . . that's not what everyone else sees.

Name: Vision
Line: [He touches the mind stone in his forehead.] Do you know, I don't know what this is? [It glows.] Not really. I know it's not of this world, that it powered Loki's staff, gave you your abilities, but . . . its true nature is a mystery. And yet, it is part of me.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Are you afraid of it?

Name: Vision
Line: I wish to understand it. The more I do, the less it controls me. One day . . . who knows? I may even control it.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: [Wanda looks at the food.] I don't know what's in this but it is not paprika. I'm gonna go to the store. I'll be back in 20 minutes.

Name: Vision
Line: Alternatively, we could order a pizza?

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Vision, are you not letting me leave?

Name: Vision
Line: [He blocks her way.] It is a question of safety.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: I can protect myself.

Name: Vision
Line: [He holds her arm.] Not yours. Mr. Stark would like to avoid the possibility of another public incident. Until the Accords are on a . . . more secured foundation.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: And what do you want?

Name: Vision
Line: For people to see you . . . as I do. [She looks at him gravely.]

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: So, you like cats?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Sam.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: What? Dude shows up dressed like a cat and you don't wanna know more?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Your suit . . . t's Vibranium?

Name: T'Challa
Line: [T'Challes eyes narrow as he glances sideways.] The Black Panther has been the protector of Wakanda for generations. A mantle, passed from warrior to warrior. And now, because your friend murdered my father, I also wear the mantle of king. So, I ask you . . . as both warrior and king . . . how long do you think you can keep your friend safe from me? [Steve is stony faced as the convoy heads underground.]

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: What's gonna happen to him?

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: This is Everett Ross, Deputy Task Force Commander.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: What about our lawyer?

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: I better not look out the window and see anybody flying around in that. [As they go Steve looks back and catches Bucky's eye.]

Name: T'Challa
Line: I don't intend on going anywhere.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: For the record, this is what making things worse looks like.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: He's alive.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [on his phone] No. Romania was not Accords-sanctioned. And, Colonel Rhodes is supervising cleanup.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Try not to break anything while we fix this.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [still on the phone.] Consequences? You bet there'll be consequences. Obviously you can quote me on that 'cause I just said it. Anything else? Thank you, sir.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: 'Consequences'?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Secretary Ross wants you both prosecuted. Had to give him something.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: I'm not getting that shield back, am I?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Technically, it's the government's property. Wings, too.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: That's cold.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Warmer than jail.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Hey, you wanna see something cool? I pulled something from Dad's archives. Felt timely. [Tony shows him two pens in a black presentation box.] FDR signed the Lend-Lease bill with these in 1941. Provided support to the Allies when they needed it most.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Some would say it brought our country closer to war.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: See? If not for these, you wouldn't be here. I'm trying to . . . what do you call it? That's an olive branch. Is that what you call it?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Is Pepper here? I didn't see her.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: We're kinda . . . well, not kinda . . .

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Pregnant?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: No. Definitely not. We're taking a break. It's nobody's fault.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: I'm so sorry, Tony. I didn't know.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: A few years ago, I almost lost her, so I trashed all my suits. Then, we had to mop up HYDRA . . . and then Ultron. My fault. And then, and then, and then, I never stopped. Because the truth is I don't wanna stop. I don't wanna lose her. I thought maybe the Accords could split the difference. [Tony stands up and paces.] In her defense, I'm a handful. Yet, Dad was a pain in the ass, but he and Mom always made it work.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You know, I'm glad Howard got married. I only knew him when he was young and single.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Oh, really? You two knew each other? He never mentioned that. Maybe only a thousand times. God, I hated you.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: I don't mean to make things difficult.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I know, because you're a very polite person.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: If I see a situation pointed south . . . I can't ignore it. Sometimes I wish I could.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: No, you don't.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Steve smiles thinly.] No, I don't. Sometimes . . .

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Sometimes I wanna punch you in your perfect teeth. But I don't wanna see you gone. We need you, Cap. So far, nothing's happened that can't be undone, if you sign. We can make the last 24 hours legit. Barnes gets transferred to an American psych-center . . . instead of a Wakandan prison.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Steve frowns thoughtfully and picks up one of the fountain pens. He stands up and paces, then turns to Tony. In the control room beyond there are multiple screens on the walls.] I'm not saying it's impossible, but there would have to be safeguards.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Sure. Once we put out the PR fire, those documents can be amended. I'd file a motion to have you and Wanda reinstated . . .

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Wanda? What about Wanda?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: She's fine. She's confined to the compound, currently. Vision's keeping her company.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Oh God, Tony! Every time. Every time I think you see things the right way . . .

Name: Tony Stark
Line: What? It's a 100 acres with a lap pool. It's got a screening room. There's worse ways to protect people.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Protection? Is that how you see this? This is protection? It's internment, Tony.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: She's not a US citizen.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Oh, come on, Tony.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: And they don't grant visas to weapons of mass destruction.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: She's a kid!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: GIVE ME A BREAK! I'm doing what has to be done . . . to stave off something worse.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Steve nods faintly.] You keep telling yourself that. [He puts the pen down.] Hate to break up the set. [He leaves the office and rueful Tony watches Bucky on one of the control room's screens.]

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: [The evaluator sits at a desk facing Bucky's pod. Inside Bucky's still restrained.] Hello, Mr. Barnes. I've been sent by the United Nations to evaluate you. Do you mind if I sit? Your first name is James?

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: [In an office with Sam and Steve.] The receipt for your gear.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: 'Bird costume'? Come on.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: I didn't write it. [Sharon pushes a button witch stops the restriction on the audio from Bucky's evaluation.]

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: I'm not here to judge you. I just want to ask you a few questions. Do you know where you are, James? I can't help you if you don't talk to me, James.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: My name is Bucky.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Why would the Task Force release this photo to begin with?

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: Get the word out, involve as many eyes as we can?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Right. It's a good way to flush a guy out of hiding. Set off a bomb, get your picture taken. Get seven billion people looking for the Winter Soldier.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: You're saying someone framed him to find him.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Steve, we looked for the guy for two years and found nothing.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: We didn't bomb the UN. That turns a lot of heads.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: Yeah, but that doesn't guarantee that whoever framed him would get him. It guarantees that we would. [Sharon's gaze falls on the evaluator in the screen, her eyes narrow.]

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Steve frowns and looks around.] Yeah.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: [In the secure chamber.] Tell me, Bucky. You've seen a great deal, haven't you?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: I don't want to talk about it.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: You fear that… if you open your mouth, the horrors might never stop. Don't worry. [Zemo gets a message on his screen

Name: Tony Stark
Line: FRIDAY, get me the source of that outage.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: [In the office.] Sub-level 5, east wing. [T'Challa spots Steve and Sam bolting.]

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: What the hell is this?

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Why don't we discuss your home? Not Romania. Certainly not Brooklyn, no. I mean, your real home. [Zemo removes his glasses then walks towards Bucky reading from the red book by torchlight.] Желание. ([subtitled] Longing.)

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: [Bucky shuts his eyes.] No. [Bucky's head snaps back.]

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Ржавый. ([subtitled] Rusted.)

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: Stop.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Семнадцать. ([subtitled] Seventeen.)

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: [Bucky's metal arm trembles in its restraint.] Stop. [He sneers angrily.]

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Рассвет. ([subtitled] Daybreak.)

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Печь. ([subtitled] Furnace.) Девять. ([subtitled] Nine.)

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Добросердечный. ([subtitled] Benign.)

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Возвращение на Родину. ([subtitled] Homecoming.) Один. ([subtitled

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Солдат? ([subtitled] Soldier?)

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: Я готов отвечать. ([subtitled] Ready to comply.)

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Mission report. December 16, 1991.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Help me. Help.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Steve finds Zemo in a heap inside the chamber.] Get up. [he grabs Zemo and shoves him against the wall.] Who are you? What do you want?

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: To see an empire fall.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Hey.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Please tell me you brought a suit.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Sure did. It's a lovely Tom Ford, three-piece, two-button. I'm an active-duty non-combatant.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: Follow me. [Sharon runs past Tony and Natasha.]

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: [on radio

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: You could at least recognize me.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Damn it. [he looks around the wide courtyard and scowls.]

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Hey, Cap! [Steve goes over to join Sam by Bucky who sits with his arm in the vice. They stare at him.]

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: Steve.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Which Bucky am I talking to?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: Your mom's name was Sarah...You used to wear newspapers in your shoes.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Can't read that in a museum.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Just like that, we're suppose to be cool?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: What did I do?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Enough.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: Oh, God, I knew this would happen. Everything HYDRA put inside me is still there. All he had to do was say the goddamn words.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Who was he?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: I don't know.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: People are dead. The bombing, the setup. The doctor did all that just to get 10 minutes with you. I need you to do better than "I don't know."

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: He wanted to know about Siberia. Where I was kept. He wanted to know exactly where.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Why would he need to know that?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: Because I'm not the only Winter Soldier.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Who were they?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: Their most elite death squad. More kills than anyone in HYDRA history. And that was before the serum.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: They all turn out like you?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: Worse.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: The doctor, could he control them?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: Enough.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Said he wanted to see an empire fall.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: With these guys he could do it. They speak 30 languages, can hide in plain sight, infiltrate, assassinate, destabilize, They can take a whole country down in one night. You'd never see them coming.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: [Sam steps up to Steve.] This would have been a lot easier a week ago.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: If we call Tony . . .

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: No, he won't believe us.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Even if he did . . .

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Who knows if the Accords would let him help.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: We're on our own.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Maybe not. I know a guy.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: I don't suppose you have any idea where they are?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: We will. GSG-9's got the borders covered. Recon's flying 24/7. They'll get a hit. We'll handle it.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: You don't get it, Stark. It's not yours to handle. It's clear you can't be objective. I'm putting Special Ops on this.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: What happens when the shooting starts? What, do you kill Steve Rogers?

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: If we're provoked. Barnes would've been eliminated in Romania if it wasn't for Rogers. There are dead people who would be alive now. Feel free to check my math.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: All due respect, you're not going to solve this with boys in bullets, Ross. You gotta let us bring them in.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: How would that end any differently from the last time?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Because this time, I won't be wearing loafers and a silk shirt. 72 hours, guaranteed.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: 36 hours. Barnes. Rogers. Wilson.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Thank you, sir. [Tony rubs his hand on his chest and slumps, exhaling.] My left arm is numb, is that normal?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: [She pats him on the shoulder.] You alright?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Always. [He has a massive black eye and a cut on his brow.] 36 hours, jeez.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: We're seriously understaffed.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Oh, yeah. It'd be great if we had a Hulk right about now. Any shot?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: No. You really think he'd be on our side?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: No.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: I have an idea.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Me too. Where's yours?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Downstairs. Where's yours? [Tony smiles slightly.]

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Hey, May.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Okay. This crazy car parked outside . . . [Peter sees Tony and his eyes widen.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Oh, Mr. Parker.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Um . . . [He takes out his earphones.] What--what are you doing . . .? Hey! Uh, I'm--Im--I'm Peter.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Tony.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: What are . . .what are you--what are you--what are you doing here?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: It's about time we met. You've been getting my e-mails, right?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Yeah. Yeah.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Right?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Regarding the . . .

Name: Peter Parker
Line: About the grant.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: The September Foundation.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Right.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah. Remember when you applied?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Yeah.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I approved, so now we're in business.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Why, I just, I just . . . I just know how much you love surprises, so I thought I would let you know . . . wh . . . anyway, what did I apply for?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: That's what I'm here to hash out.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Okay. Hash, hash out, okay.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: It's so hard for me to believe that she's someone's aunt.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: This walnut date loaf is exceptional.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Let me just stop you there.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Is this grant, like, got money involved or whatever? No?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Yeah?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: It's pretty well funded.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Wow.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Look who you're talking to. Can I have 5 minutes with him?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [In Peter's bedroom Tony bolts the door and spits out the walnut loaf.] As walnut date loaves go, that wasn't bad. [He notices Peter's collection of old computers.] Whoa, what do we have here? Retro tech, huh? Thrift store? Salvation Army?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Uh, the garbage, actually.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You're a dumpster diver.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Yeah, I was . . . anyway, look, um, I definitely did not apply for your grant.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Ah-ah! Me first.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Okay.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Quick question of the rhetorical variety. [He pulls out his phone which projects a video of Peter Parker in his Spider-Man outfit.] That's you, right?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Um, no. What do you. What do you mean?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah. Look at you go. Wow! Nice catch. 3,000 pounds, 40 miles an hour. That's not easy. You got mad skills.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: That's all- That's all on YouTube, though, right? I mean, that's where you found that? Because you know that's all fake. It's all done on the computer.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Mm-Hmm.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: It's like that video. What is it?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah . . . oh, you mean like those UFOs over Phoenix?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Exactly.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Oh, what have we here?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [Peter hides his Spider-Man suit.] Uh . . . that's a . . .

Name: Tony Stark
Line: So. You're the . . . Spider . . . ling. Crime-fighting Spider . . .you're Spider-Boy?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [Peter folds his arms petulantly.] S . . . Spider-Man.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Not in that onesie, you're not.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: It's not a onesie. [Tony picks up the suit.] I don't believe this. I was actually having a real good day today, you know, Mr. Stark. Didn't miss my train, this perfectly good DVD player was just sitting there and . . . Algebra test. Nailed it!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Who else knows? Anybody?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Nobody.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Not even your . . . unusually attractive aunt?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: No. No, no. No, no. If she knew, she would freak out. And when she freaks out, I freak out.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You know what I think is really cool? This webbing. That tensile strength is off the charts. Who manufactured that?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: I did.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Climbing the walls, how you doing that? Adhesive gloves?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: It's a long story. I was uh . . .

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Lordy! Can you even see in these?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Yes. Yes, I can! I can. I can-I can see in those. Okay? It's just that… when whatever happened, happened . . . it's like my senses have been dialed to 11. There's way too much input, so . . . they just kinda help me focus.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You're in dire need of an upgrade. Systemic, top to bottom. 100-point restoration. That's why I'm here. [Peter sits on his bed and looks at Tony.] Why you doing this? I gotta know. What's your MO? What gets you outta that twin bed in the morning?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Because . . . [he fiddles with his fingers] because l've been me my whole life, and l've had these powers for 6 months.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Mm-Hmm.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: I read books, I build computers . . . and--and yeah. I would love to play football. But I couldn't then so I shouldn't now.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Sure, because you're different.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Exactly. But I can't tell anybody that, so I'm not. When you can do the things that I can, but you don't . . . [Tony leans closer.] and then the bad things happen . . . they happen because of you.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [he looks affected by Peter's words.] So you wanna look out for the little guy? You wanna do your part? Make the world a better place, all that, right?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Yeah. Yeah just looking out . . . for the little guy. That's--that's what it is.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [He slowly steps over to Peter whose leg is stretched out on the bed. Tony looks down at it.] I'm gonna sit here, so you move the leg. [Peter moves along. Tony sits beside him and raises his hand. He hesitantly clasps Peter's shoulder.] You got a passport?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Uh, no. I don't even have a driver's license.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You ever been to Germany?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: No.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Oh, you'll love it.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: I can't go to Germany!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Why?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: I got . . . homework.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I'm gonna pretend you didn't say that.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: I'm---I'm being serious! I can't just drop out of school!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Might be a little dangerous. Better tell Aunt Hottie I'm taking you on a field trip.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [He webs Tony's hand to the door.] Don't tell Aunt May.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Alright, Spider-Man. [They share an earnest look before Tony returns to his usual attitude.] Get me out of this.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Sorry, I'll get the . . .

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: What is it?

Name: Vision
Line: Stay here, please.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Guess I shoulda knocked.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Oh my god! What are you doing here?

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Disappointing my kids. [He shoots arrows to both sides of the room.] I'm supposed to go water-skiing. Cap needs our help. Come on.

Name: Vision
Line: Clint! [Wanda and Clint stop.] You should not be here.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: [He turns around.] Really? I retire for, what, like five minutes, and it all goes to shit.

Name: Vision
Line: Please consider the consequences of your actions.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Okay, they're considered. Okay, we gotta go. [Vision is held in a force field, crackling and sparkling between the two arrows.] It's this way.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: I've caused enough problems.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: [Frowning Clint runs back from the door.] You gotta help me, Wanda. Look, you wanna mope, can go to high school. You wanna make amends, you get off your ass. Shit. [Vision breaks the force field with his mind stone. He punches Clint to the floor, Clint recovers quickly.] I knew I should've stretched. [He extends a baton and tries to hit Vision, but the blows go through him. Clint resorts to punches, then tries the baton again. It breaks. Clint tries to kick Vision, but his leg goes right through him. Vision gets Clint in a headlock.]

Name: Vision
Line: Clint, you can't overpower me.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: I know I can't. But she can.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Vision, that's enough. Let him go. I'm leaving.

Name: Vision
Line: I can't let you.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: [She holds her hands apart, glowing with energy. Clint slips from Vision's grasp.] I'm sorry.

Name: Vision
Line: [He falters.] If you do this . . . they will never stop being afraid of you.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: I can't control their fear, only my own. [She moves closer. Vision glows from within and crashes through the floor, and several floors beneath. Wanda and Clint stand over the holes in the floors.]

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Oh . . . come on. We got one more stop.

Name: T'Challa
Line: As entertaining as that would be . . .

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: You really think you can find him?

Name: T'Challa
Line: My resources are considerable.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Yeah, it took the world 70 years to find Barnes . . . so you could probably do that in about half the time.

Name: T'Challa
Line: You know where they are.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: I know someone who does.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: Not sure you understand the concept of a getaway car.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: It's low profile.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: Good, because this stuff tends to draw a crowd. [She opens the trunk of her car, revealing Steve's and Sams's gear.]

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: [He sits behind Sam in the getaway car.] Can you move your seat up?

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: No.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: I owe you again.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: Keeping a list. [She glances at Bucky.] You know, he kinda tried to kill me.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Sorry. I'll put it on the list, too. They're going to come looking for you.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: I know.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Thank you, Sharon.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: That was . . .

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Late.

Name: Sharon Carter
Line: Damn right. I should go.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Okay.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Cap.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You know I wouldn't have called If I had any other choice.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Hey man, you're doing me a favor. Besides, I owe a debt.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Thanks for having my back.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: It was time to get off my ass.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: How about our other recruit?

Name: Clint Barton
Line: He's rarin' to go. Had to put a little coffee in him, but… he should be good.

Name: Scott Lang
Line: What timezone is this?

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Come on. Come on.

Name: Scott Lang
Line: [Scott shakes Steve's hand with an amazed look.] Captain America.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Mr. Lang.

Name: Scott Lang
Line: It's an honor. I'm shaking your hand too long. Wow! This is awesome! Captain America. [He looks at Wanda.] I know you, too. You're great! [He turns back and feels Steve's shoulders.] Jeez. Ah, look, I wanna say, I know you know a lot of super people, so . . . thinks for thanking of me. [(sic!) To Sam.] Hey, man!

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: What's up, Tic Tac?

Name: Scott Lang
Line: Uh, good to see you. Look, what happened last time when I . . .

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: It was a great audition, but it'll . . . it'll never happen again.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: They tell you what we're up against?

Name: Scott Lang
Line: Something about some . . . psycho-assassins?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: We're outside the law on this one. So, if you come with us, you're a wanted man.

Name: Scott Lang
Line: Yeah, well, what else is new?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: We should get moving.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: We got a chopper lined up.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: They're evacuating the airport.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Stark.

Name: Scott Lang
Line: Stark?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Suit up.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Wow, it's so weird how you run into people at the airport. Don't you think that's weird?

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Definitely weird.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Hear me out, Tony. That doctor, the psychiatrist, he's behind all of this.

Name: T'Challa
Line: [T'Challa leaps over a truck.] Captain.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Your highness.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Anyway, Ross gave me 36 hours to bring you in. That was 24 hours ago. Can you help a brother out?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You're after the wrong guy.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Your judgment is askew. Your old war buddy killed innocent people yesterday.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: And there are five more super soldiers just like him. I can't let the doctor find them first, Tony. I can't.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Steve . . . you know what's about to happen. Do you really wanna punch your way out of this one?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: All right, I've run out of patience. Underoos! [Peter shoots a web, stealing Steve's shield and binding his hands.] Nice job, kid.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Thanks. Well, I could've stuck the landing a little better. It's just the new suit… Well, it's nothing, Mr. Stark. It's--it's perfect. Thank you.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah, we don't really need to start a conversation.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Okay. Cap . . . Captain. Big fan, I'm Spider-Man.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah, we'll talk about it later. Just . . .

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Hey, everyone.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: . . . Good job.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You've been busy.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: And you've been a complete idiot. Dragging in Clint. 'Rescuing' Wanda from a place she doesn't even want to leave, a safe place. I'm trying to keep . . . I'm trying to keep you from tearing the Avengers apart.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You did that when you signed.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Alright, We're done. You're gonna turn Barnes over, you're gonna come with us. NOW! Because it's us! Or a squad of J-SOC guys . . . with no compunction about being impolite. [Steve looks aside.] Come on.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: [He radios Steve.] We found it. Their Quinjet's in hanger five, north runway.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Steve holds his hands up and Clint shoots the web off.] Alright, Lang.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Hey, guys, something . . .

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Whoa. What--what the hell was that?

Name: Scott Lang
Line: [He retrieves Steve's shield.] I believe this is yours, Captain America.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Oh, great. Alright, there's two on the parking deck. One of them's Maximoff, I'm gonna grab her. Rhodey, you want to take Cap?

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Got two in the terminal, Wilson and Barnes.

Name: T'Challa
Line: Barnes is mine!

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Hey, Mr. Stark, what should I do?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: What we discussed. Keep your distance. Web 'em up.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Okay, copy that!

Name: T'Challa
Line: Move, Captain. I won't ask a second time.

Name: Scott Lang
Line: [He faces Natasha.] Look, I really don't want to hurt you.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: I wouldn't stress about it. [She kicks him in the groin and he miniaturizes, throwing her head over heels. She zaps him off her wrist and he slams into a nearby truck, laving a small dent.]

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: [In the terminal.] What the hell is that?

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Everyone's got a gimmick now.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [Peter swings through the glass wall and kicks Sam backwards. Bucky throws a punch, Peter catches his fist.] You have a metal arm? That is awesome, dude! [Sam hits Peter.] You have the right to remain silent! [Mid-air Peter fends Sam off, then swings after him using his webs.]

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Sorry, Cap. This won't kill you but it ain't gonna tickle either. [He smacks Steve's shield with a mace.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Hovering above the ground.] Wanda, I think you hurt Vision's feelings.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: You locked me in my room.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Okay. First, that's an exaggeration. Second, I did it to protect you. Hey, Clint.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Hey, man.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Clearly, retirement doesn't suit you. You got tired of shooting golf?

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Well, I played 18, I shot 18. Just can't seem to miss. [He fires an arrow which Tony deflects.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: First time for everything.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Made you look.

Name: FRIDAY
Line: Multiple contusions detected.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah, I detected that too.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Oh god. [Bucky throws something at him.] Hey buddy, I think you lost this! [Peter throws it back. Sam kicks him off the beam and Peter fires a web which sends Sam crashing to the floor. Peter webs Sam's wrist to a balcony railing.] Those wings carbon fiber?

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Is this stuff coming out of you?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: That would explain the rigidity-flexibility ratio, which, gotta say, that's awesome, man.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: I don't know if you've been a fight before but there's usually not this much talking.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Alright, sorry, my bad. [He swings down and Bucky jumps in the way. Bucky and Sam fall through the glass down onto the next floor and Peter webs them.] Guys, look. I'd love to keep this up but I've only got one job here today and I gotta impress Mr. Stark, so, I'm really sorry. [Redwing drags Peter through the glass wall.] Wwahhhh!

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: You couldn't have done that earlier?

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: I hate you.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Great.

Name: Scott Lang
Line: Hey, Cap, heads up! [He throws Steve a miniature truck.] Throw it at this. Now! [Steve throws it and the truck enlarges, tumbling towards War Machine.]

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Oh, come on! [The truck lands and explodes.]

Name: Scott Lang
Line: Oh, man. I thought it was a water truck. Uh . . . sorry. [Scott and Steve run off.]

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Alright. Now, I'm pissed.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: [Tony helps her up.] Is this, part of the plan?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Well, my plan was to go easy on them. You wanna switch it up?

Name: Clint Barton
Line: [To Wanda as he spots the Quinjet.] There's our ride.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Come on!

Name: Vision
Line: Captain Rogers. I know you believe what you're doing is right. But for the collective good you must surrender now. [Tony's team arrives.]

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: What do we do, Cap?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: We fight.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: This is gonna end well. [The two teams stride towards each other with grim determination etched on their faces.]

Name: Peter Parker
Line: They're not stopping.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Neither are we. [Everyone breaks into a sprint.]

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: We're still friends, right?

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Depends on how hard you hit me. [She spins him with her legs. As she's about to kick his head, her foot stops and glows bright red. Wanda projects Natasha down.]

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: You were pulling your punches. [Clint nods sheepishly.]

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: [Bucky and T'Challa have each other by the throat.] I didn't kill your father.

Name: T'Challa
Line: Then why did you run? [T'Challa pulls Bucky's hand off his neck, then spins him and fly-kicks him backwards. He sprouts claws and aims for Bucky's neck, but Wanda stops his hand, then waves her arms and sends T'Challa crashing into a passenger gangway.]

Name: Peter Parker
Line: That thing does not obey the laws of physics at all.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Look kid. There's a lot going on here that you don't understand.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Mr. Stark said you'd say that. Wow. [he fires webs which stick to Steve's shield and ankle. He pulls and Steve slides towards him. Peter kicks him backwards, then rolls clear.] He also said to go for your legs. [As Steve runs to get his shield, Peter webs his hands and pulls. Steve grits his teeth, spins and somersaults, propelling Peter through the air.]

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: [Evading fire from Iron Man.] Clint, can you get him off me?

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Buckled in?

Name: Scott Lang
Line: Yeah. No, I'm good. I'm good, Arrow Guy. Let's go. Let's go! [Miniaturized Scott is on the tip of Clint's arrow. As he fires it, the head splits and Iron Man shoots the shards. Scott dives between Iron Man's splayed fingers and slips inside the Iron Man Suit at the shoulder joint.]

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Steve catches a web and tugs Peter towards him, knocking him down with the shield. Peter recovers and pulls himself up on top of a gangway.] Stark tell you anything else?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: That you're wrong. You think you're right. That makes you dangerous. [He swings down and Steve leaps to kick him backwards onto the gangway's leg.]

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Guess he had a point. [He throws his shield at the leg and the gangway falls. Peter holds it up.] You got heart, kid. Where're you from?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Queens.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Brooklyn. [Steve leaves Peter holding the gangway.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Clint fires arrows at hovering Iron Man whose arm-lasers malfunction.] Friday?

Name: FRIDAY
Line: We have some weapon systems offline.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: They what?

Name: Scott Lang
Line: Oh, you're gonna have to take this into the shop.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Who's speaking?

Name: Scott Lang
Line: It's your conscience. We don't talk a lot these days.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Friday?

Name: FRIDAY
Line: Deploying fire suppression system.

Name: Scott Lang
Line: Uh -oh. Oh boy. Whoa! [Inside the suit Scott sprints through narrow banks of components, chased by a rolling cloud of CO2. He's ejected from the suit.]

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: [To Steve.] We gotta go. That guy's probably in Siberia by now.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: We gotta draw out the flyers. I'll take Vision. You get to the jet.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: No, you get to the jet! Both of you! [Being chased by War Machine.] The rest of us aren't getting out of here.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: As much as I hate to admit it, if we're gonna win this one, some of us might have to lose it.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: This isn't the real fight, Steve.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Alright, Sam, what's the play?

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: We need a diversion, something big.

Name: Scott Lang
Line: I got something kind of big, but I can't hold it very long. On my signal, run like hell. And if I tear myself in half . . . don't come back for me.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: He's gonna tear himself in half?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You're sure about this, Scott?

Name: Scott Lang
Line: I do it all the time. I mean once . . . in a lab. Then I passed out. I'm the boss. I'm the boss. I'm the boss. I'm the boss. I'm the BOSS! [He leaps from mobile stairs and lands on War Machine's back as he flies past. He operates his suit's wrist, shuts his eyes and activates a remote. Scott grows into a towering Behemoth and grabs War Machine's leg.]

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Holy shit!

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Okay, tiny dude is big now. He's big now.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: I guess that's the signal.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Way to go, Tic Tac!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Give me back my Rhodey. [Sam flies feet first into Iron Man.]

Name: Peter Parker
Line: I got him! [Scott sends War Machine flying and Peter catches him with a web.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Okay, anybody on our side hiding any shocking and fantastic abilities they'd like to disclose, I'm open to suggestion.

Name: Scott Lang
Line: You wanna get to them… you gotta go through me. [He sweeps his gigantic foot through the crates T'Challa's standing on, smashing them to pieces. Scott is engulfed in explosions as War Machine swoops towards him with Peter clinging to a web stuck to War Machine's back. He fires more webs and wraps them around Scott's over-sized arms.]

Name: Clint Barton
Line: We haven't met yet. [He flattens his bow and spins it around.] I'm Clint.

Name: T'Challa
Line: I don't care. [Wielding the bow like a staff Clint attacks T'Challa who a acrobatically ducks then counters with a high kick.]

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Ahhh! [Wanda waves her hands flinging vehicles into War Machines path.]

Name: Scott Lang
Line: Get off. [Distracted by Peter Ant-Man doesn't spot Vision curling into a ball and ramming into him. Vision spots Steve and Bucky approaching the hangar as Ant-Man wavers. He simply floats through Ant-Man's chest. Something just flew in me! [Vision fires a shining beam of energy from his mind stone and the control tower collapses towards the entrance of the hangar. Wanda struggles to slow its collapse. Then War Machine descends behind her fires a sonic disruptor. Wanda holds her head and screams. The tower falls all around Steve and Bucky, but they make it into the hangar where Natasha is waiting for them.]

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: You're not gonna stop.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You know I can't.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: I'm gonna regret this. [She stuns T'Challa who's arrived behind them.] Go. [Steve and Bucky run for the Quinjet as she keeps T'Challa at bay.]

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [Outside] Hey, guys, you ever see that really old movie, Empire Strikes Back?

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Jesus, Tony, how old is this guy?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I don't know, I didn't carbon-date him. He's on the young side.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [He swings towards Ant-Man.] You know that part . . . where they're on the snow planet . . . with the walking thingies? [He wraps webs around Scott's legs.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Maybe the kid's on to something.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: High now, Tony. Go high.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [He swings around and around Ant-Man's legs as Iron Man and War Machine power towards his head, both landing blows together.] YES! Ha ha! That was awesome! [Giant Ant-Man topples. A flailing limb catching Peter and knocking him flying just before Scott slams into the ground on his back. He returns to normal size and removes the face-plate of his helmet, grimacing.]

Name: Scott Lang
Line: Does anyone have any orange slices?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [He lands by Peter who's in a heap. Retracting the helmet Tony looks concerned.] Kid, you alright?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Hey! Get off me!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Same side. Guess who. Hi. It's me.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Oh. Hey, man.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: That was scary.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah. You're done. Alright?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: What?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You did a good job. Stay down.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: No, I'm good. I'm fine.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Stay down.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: No, it's good I gotta get him back!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You're going home or I'll call Aunt May! You're done!

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Wait. Mr. Stark, wait! I'm not done, I'm not . . . [He slumps down.] Okay, I'm done. I'm done.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: [In the partially wrecked hangar the Quinjet's engines fire and the guns blast debris from the entrance. Natasha keeps T'Challa held until the jet rises. Black Panther leaps, but can't keep hold and the Quinjet flies out of the hangar. War Machine flies after it. In the hangar

Name: Vision
Line: [Outside Vision kneels beside Wanda and gently holds her in his arms. She pants for breath.] I'm sorry.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Me, too.

Name: Vision
Line: It's as I said. Catastrophe.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Vision, I got a bandit on my six. [Falcon fires small explosives which erupt and buffet War Machine.] Vision! You copy? Target his thrusters, turn him into a glider.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Rhodey! [Iron Man and Falcon dive.]

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Tony, I'm flying dead stick. [As he plunges the suit emits black smoke. Iron Man swoops down towards him. Rhodes' eyes start to close.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: RHODES! [Mar Machine smacks into a wide, grassy field just before Iron Man lands nearby. His helmet retracts and he pulls off War Machine's face plate. Rhodes' eyes are closed and there's blood on his face.] Read vitals.

Name: FRIDAY
Line: Heartbeat detected. Emergency medical is on its way.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: [He swoops down and lands on his feet. His wings retract.] I'm sorry. [Tony zaps Falcon backwards with a blast of energy from the palm of his suit. Vision glides to the ground just in front of Falcon. Stony faced Tony remains with his arms around War Machine.]

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Guten Morgen Frau Leiber. Zimmer 201 hier (Good morning, Mrs. Leiber. [subtitled] This is room 201.)

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Wie gut Sie mich kennen. ([subtitled] You know me so well.)

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: What's gonna happen to your friends?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Steve stares ahead, heavyhearted. He sighs and shakes his head.] Whatever it is… I'll deal with it.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: [He looks thoughtful.] I don't know if I'm worth all this, Steve.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [He glances around at Bucky.] What you did all those years . . . it wasn't you. You didn't have a choice.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: I know. But I did it.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: How did this happen?

Name: Vision
Line: I became distracted.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I didn't think that was possible.

Name: Vision
Line: Neither did I. [Tony leaves Vision looking in on Rhodes. Along the corridor Tony spots an equally concerned Natasha.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: The doctors say he shattered L4 through S1. Extreme laceration in the spinal cord. Probably looking at some form of paralysis.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Steve's not gonna stop. If you don't either, Rhodey's gonna be the best case scenario.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You let them go, Nat.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: We played this wrong.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: 'We'? Boy, it must be hard to shake the whole double agent thing, huh? It sticks in the DNA.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Are you incapable of letting go of your ego for one goddamn second?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: T'Challa told Ross what you did, so . . . they're coming for you.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: I'm not the one that needs to watch their back. [She walks away.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [He activates holographic images appearing on his wrist device.] What am I looking at, Friday?

Name: FRIDAY
Line: Priority upload from Berlin police.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Fire up the chopper.

Name: FRIDAY
Line: The Task Force called for a psychiatrist as soon as Barnes was captured. The UN dispatched Dr. Theo Broussard from Geneva within the hour. He was met by this man.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Did you run facial recognition yet?

Name: FRIDAY
Line: What do I look like?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Uh, I don't know. I've been picturing a red head.

Name: FRIDAY
Line: You must be thinking of someone else.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Must be.

Name: FRIDAY
Line: The fake doctor is actually Colonel Helmut Zemo, Sokovian Intelligence. [Tony projects the image.] Zemo ran Echo Skorpion, a Sokovian covert kill squad.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: So, what happened to the real Broussard?

Name: FRIDAY
Line: He was found dead in a Berlin hotel room. Where police also found a wig and facial prosthesis approximating the appearance of one James Buchanan Barnes.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Son of a bitch. Get this to Ross.

Name: FRIDAY
Line: Yes, Boss.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: So? You got the files? Let's reroute the satellites, start facial scanning for this Zemo guy.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: You seriously think I'm gonna listen to you after that fiasco in Leipzig? You're lucky you're not in one of these cells. [Ross looks at Tony sternly and leads on through a thick, steel security door. Soldiers stand guard in an operations room. Tony looks at a surveillance screen. it shows Wanda, sitting hunched and bedraggled in a cramped prison cell.]

Name: Clint Barton
Line: [clapping] The Futurist, gentlemen! The Futurist is here! He sees all! He knows what's best for you, whether your like it or not.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Give me a break, Barton. I had no idea they'll put you here. Come on.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: [spits] Yeah, well, you knew they'd put us somewhere, Tony.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah, but not some super-max floating ocean pokey. You know, this place is for maniacs. This is a place for . . .

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Criminals? [He stands up.] Criminals, Tony. Think that's the word you're looking for. [He eyes Tony through the bars.] Right? That didn't used to mean me. Or Sam, or Wanda. But here we are.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Because you broke the law.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: Yeah.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I didn't make you.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: La, la, la, la, la . . .

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You read it, you broke it.

Name: Clint Barton
Line: La, la, la, la la…

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Alright, you're all grown up, you got a wife and kids. I don't understand, why didn't you think about them before you chose the wrong side? [He walks away.]

Name: Clint Barton
Line: You gotta watch your back with this guy. There's a chance he's gonna break it.

Name: Scott Lang
Line: Hank Pym always said, you never can trust a Stark.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Who are you?

Name: Scott Lang
Line: Come on, man.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: How's Rhodes?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: They're flying him to Columbia Medical tomorrow. So . . . fingers cross. [Sam shakes his head.]What do you need? They feed you yet?

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: [He raises his eyebrows.] You're the good cop now?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I'm just the guy who needs to know where Steve went.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Well, you better go get a bad cop, because you're gonna have to go Mark Fuhrman on my ass to get information out of me.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Oh, I just knocked the 'A' out of their 'AV'. We got about 30 seconds before they realize it's not their equipment.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: [In the operations room.] What did you do? Get it back up!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Back in the cell.] Just look. Because that is the fellow who was supposed to interrogate Barnes. [He shoes a holographic image of Doctor Broussard.] Clearly, I made a mistake. Sam, I was wrong.

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: That's a first.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Cap is definitely off the reservation but he's about to need all the help he can get. We don't know each other very well. You don't have to…

Name: Sam Wilson
Line: Hey, it's alright. [Tony leans closer to the window. Sam sighs and looks uneasy.] Look, I'll tell you… but you have to go alone and as a friend.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Easy.

Name: Secretary Ross
Line: Stark? Did he give you anything on Rogers?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Nope. Told me to go to hell. I'm going back to the compound instead, but you can call me anytime. I'll put you on hold, I like to watch the line blink. [Ross stares at Tony who smiles as he gets in the chopper and the door slides shut. The chopper rises off the helipad and flies away. The doors close on the prison roof.]

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You remember that time we had to ride back from Rockaway Beach in the back of that freezer truck?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: Was that the time we used our train money to buy hot dogs?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You blew three bucks trying to win that stuffed bear for a redhead.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: What was her name again?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Dolores. You called her Doll.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: She's gotta be a hundred years old right now.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: So are we, pal. [He clamps his hand on Bucky's shoulder.]

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: He can't have been here more than a few hours.

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: Long enough to wake them up.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You ready?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: Yeah.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You seem a little defensive.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: It's been a long day.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: At ease, Soldier. I'm not currently after you.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Then why are you here?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Could be your story's not so crazy. Maybe. Ross has no idea I'm here. I'd like to keep it that way. Otherwise, I gotta arrest myself.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Well, that sounds like a lot of paperwork. [He lowers his shield.] It's good to see you, Tony.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You too, Cap. [to Bucky] Hey, Manchurian Candidate, you're killing me. There's a truce here. You can drop . . . [Steve signs Bucky to lower his weapon and he does.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I got heat signatures.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: How many?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Uh, one.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: [on speaker] If it's any comfort, they died in their sleep. [All of the enhanced soldiers have been shot in the head. Bucky stares at Josef's corpse.] Did you really think I wanted more of you?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: What the hell?

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: I'm grateful to them, though. They brought you here. [Zemo appears in a control room. Steve hurls his shield but it flies back.] Please, Captain. The Soviets built this chamber to withstand the launch blast of UR-100 rockets.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I'm betting I could beat that.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Oh, I'm sure you could, Mr. Stark. Given time. But then you'd never know why you came.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You killed innocent people in Vienna just to bring us here? [Black Panther watches from the shadows. Steve looks at Zemo through a window.]

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: I thought about nothing else for over a year. I studied you. I followed you. But now that you're standing here, I just realized . . . there's a bit of green in the blue of your eyes. How nice to find a flaw.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: You're Sokovian. Is that what this is about?

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Sokovia was a failed state long before you blew it to hell. No. I'm here because I made a promise.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [He studies Zemo.] You lost someone?

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: [He looks grave, clicks his tongue.] I lost everyone. And so will you. [He plays surveillance footage from December 16th 1991. Steve steps over to the screen.] An empire toppled by its enemies can rise again. But one which crumples from within? That's dead . . . forever.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [He looks at the freeze frame of a secluded road and the date, December 16 1991. His eyes rove, anxiously.] I know that road. What is this?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Tony. Tony.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Consumed with grief and tears glistening in his eyes he turns and looks at Steve.] Did you know?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: I didn't know it was him.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Don't bullshit me, Rogers! Did you know?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Yes.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [to Bucky] Get out of here!

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: It wasn't him, Tony. Hydra had control of his mind!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Move!

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: It wasn't him!

Name: FRIDAY
Line: Left boot jet failing. Flight systems compromised.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Ah crap.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: He's not going to stop. Go.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Come on, come on.

Name: FRIDAY
Line: Targeting system's knackered, boss.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I'm eyeballing it. [His helmet retracts and he shuts one eye, taking aim at the opening hatch. He fires and hits the giant hinge which explodes, cutting of Bucky's escape route. He flies up, blocks two swings from an iron pipe from Bucky, then grabs him around the neck from behind.] Do you even remember them?

Name: Bucky Barnes
Line: I remember all of them.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: This isn't gonna change what happened.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I don't care. He killed my mom.

Name: T'Challa
Line: [Sneaks up behind him] I almost kill the wrong man.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: Hardly an innocent one.

Name: T'Challa
Line: This is all you wanted? To see them rip each other apart.

Name: Helmut Zemo
Line: [Deletes the voice message] My father lived outside the city. I thought we would be safe there. My son was excited. He could see the Iron Man from the car window. I told my wife, "Don't worry. They are fighting in the city. We're miles from harm." When the dust cleared . . . and the screaming stopped. It took me two days until I found their bodies. My father . . . still holding my wife and son in his arms. And the Avengers? They went home. I knew I couldn't kill them. More powerful men than me have tried.
